@page "/about"

<div class="container mt-4">
    <h3>About</h3>
    <p>
        The HBITS Scale app is a research tool designed to help users explore contractor rates across job titles and skill levels
        as published under the NYS HBITS (Hourly-Based IT Services) program.
    </p>

    <h4>Developer</h4>
    <p>
        This application was developed by Rj's, with the goal of improving transparency and simplifying access to HBITS rate data.
    </p>

    <h4>Disclaimer</h4>
    <div class="alert alert-warning small">
        This app is for research and informational use only. Data may be incomplete, outdated, or derived from unofficial sources.
        It is not affiliated with any Contractor or government agency. Please verify all information independently before use.
    </div>

</div>
